modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 15, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104rsn1665703174361.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rsn1665703174361.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/rsn1665703174361.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"rsn1665703174361\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A security driver must perform the action requested of it, as defined by the <code class=\"ph codeph\">Function</code> member of the <code class=\"ph codeph\">USecDrv</code> structure. Some actions are applicable to both client/server and SMTP security drivers, others are specific to one or the other.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"rsn1665703174361__section_w2056ab1b5b1_w2057ab1b5_w2058ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Actions Specified by the Function Member</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__1\">\n Function\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__3\">\n Client/Server\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__4\">\n SMTP\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ety1665702678389.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ety1665702678389.html\" title=\"Determines the function codes that are valid for this driver.\">USEC_DRVINFO</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__2\">\n Specify this security driver's functionality.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__3\">\n X\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__4\">\n X\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"eef1665703174430.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eef1665703174430.html\" title=\"Authenticate the user name and password combination.\">USEC_AUTHENTICATE</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__2\">\n Authenticate the username and password combination.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__3\">\n X\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__4\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sym1665702678457.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sym1665702678457.html\" title=\"Driver is responsible for releasing any resources it acquired.\">USEC_CLOSE</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__2\">Release any resources the driver acquired. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__3\">\n X\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__4\">\n X\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ytr1665703174503.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ytr1665703174503.html\" title=\"Provide authentication information.\">USEC_USERPASSINFO</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__2\">\n Provide authentication information, such as\n <div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">\"Your password will expire in <var class=\"keyword varname\">x</var> days\"</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__3\">\n X\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__4\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"iow1665703174572.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iow1665703174572.html\" title=\"Change the password for a given user.\">USEC_PASSCHNG</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__2\">\n Change the password for a given user.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__3\">\n X\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__4\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"guy1665703174644.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/guy1665703174644.html\" title=\"Encode the contents of InBuf and place the result in OutBuf.\">USEC_ENCODE</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__2\">Encode the contents of <code class=\"ph codeph\">InBuf</code>\n                        and place the result in <code class=\"ph codeph\">OutBuf</code>. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__3\">\n X\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__4\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ptk1665703174714.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ptk1665703174714.html\" title=\"Decode the contents of InBuf and place the result in OutBuf.\">USEC_DECODE</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__2\">Decode the contents of <code class=\"ph codeph\">InBuf</code>\n                        and place the result in <code class=\"ph codeph\">OutBuf</code>. </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__3\">\n X\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__4\"></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gca1665703174791.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gca1665703174791.html\" title=\"Indicates whether the specified ESMTP extension is supported.\">USEC_VERIFY</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__2\">\n Indicate whether the specified ESMTP extension is supported.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__4\">\n X\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"njm1665702678320.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/njm1665702678320.html\" title=\"Prepares the messages that are to be sent to the server in order to carry out the initialisation and authentication protocol to establish a connection.\">USEC_OPENMSG</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__2\">\n Prepare the messages that are to be used in the initialisation and authentication protocol to establish a connection.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__4\">\n X\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bye1665703174860.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bye1665703174860.html\" title=\"Builds the messages that are used in the disconnection protocol.\">USEC_CLOSEMSG</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__2\">\n Prepare the messages that are used in the disconnection protocol.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__4\">\n X\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zpe1665703174928.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zpe1665703174928.html\" title=\"Provide runtime information about the negotiated options of the current or previous connection.\">USEC_RTINFO</a>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__2\">\n Return runtime information about negotiation options.\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__3\"></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"rsn1665703174361__table_d15755e1_d15756e1_d15757e1__entry__4\">\n X\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531768\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531768\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Security Driver Functions Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 15, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 A security driver must perform the action requested of it, as defined by the Function member of the USecDrv structure. Some actions are applicable to both client/server and SMTP security drivers, others are specific to one or the other. Table 1. Actions Specified by the Function Member Function Description Client/Server SMTP USEC_DRVINFO Specify this security driver's functionality. X X USEC_AUTHENTICATE Authenticate the username and password combination. X USEC_CLOSE Release any resources the driver acquired. X X USEC_USERPASSINFO Provide authentication information, such as \"Your password will expire in x days\" Copy X USEC_PASSCHNG Change the password for a given user. X USEC_ENCODE Encode the contents of InBuf and place the result in OutBuf . X USEC_DECODE Decode the contents of InBuf and place the result in OutBuf . X USEC_VERIFY Indicate whether the specified ESMTP extension is supported. X USEC_OPENMSG Prepare the messages that are to be used in the initialisation and authentication protocol to establish a connection. X USEC_CLOSEMSG Prepare the messages that are used in the disconnection protocol. X USEC_RTINFO Return runtime information about negotiation options. X Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}